storyInfo: While on a mission, the Ursus students run into a group of bounty hunters. Gummy tries to overcome her 'bad habit' to protect her friends.

attributes.content: Gummy has many memories.
Good ones, bad ones.
Happy ones, sad ones.
And ones she can't forget, no matter what.
They're in here!
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.content: Hurry up, don't let them get away... They have food!
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.content: Lada, be careful!
attributes.name: Anna

attributes.content: Grrr, what a bunch of pests! Anna, Lada, stay behind me!
attributes.name: Sonya

attributes.content: Heh, you lot've got some nerve. C'mere, and we'll see who has the guts!
attributes.name: Sonya

attributes.content: Dammit, it still hurts... Why are they here again? My arm hasn't fully healed yet.
attributes.name: Rosalind

attributes.content: Hey, Sonya, why don't we have a little contest to see who can take down more gopniks?
attributes.name: Rosalind

attributes.content: Cut the bullshit... Watch out!
attributes.name: Sonya

attributes.content: Come now, this is not the time to lose focus.
attributes.name: Natalya

attributes.content: Our two generals have a job to do.
attributes.name: Natalya

attributes.content: Phew... That was a close one.
attributes.name: Anna

attributes.content: Sonya, Rosalind, watch your back.
attributes.name: Anna

attributes.content: Thanks.
attributes.name: Sonya

attributes.content: If you have the stones to sneak up on me, I guess you're ready to meet your maker!
attributes.name: Rosalind

attributes.content: D-Don't panic, don't let them intimidate you. We have the numbers...
attributes.name: Female Student

attributes.content: That's right, there's only a few of 'em! Don't give them the chance to call for help. If we all charge together, we'll be fine!
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.content: Hmph.
attributes.name: Sonya

attributes.content: (Do you have a plan? It's true, they have us outnumbered.)
attributes.name: Natalya

attributes.content: (All we can do is think up a way to break out.)
attributes.name: Anna

attributes.content: I'm sorry, but... we don't have a choice. We need that food...
attributes.name: Female Student

attributes.content: I don't want to starve... I don't want to starve to death in a place like this!
attributes.name: Female Student

attributes.content: Don't give 'em a chance to escape! Block the door!
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.content: Get 'em!
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.text: I... I want to be the one who protects everyone else.
I can do anything to protect my friends.
I will use all of my strength––

attributes.content: *cough* *cough*... These bastards, there's no end to 'em!
attributes.name: Sonya

attributes.content: Don't tell me you're throwing in the towel already?
attributes.name: Rosalind

attributes.content: Bah. Ugh, I think I lost a tooth.
attributes.name: Rosalind

attributes.content: You—
attributes.name: Sonya

attributes.content: Wait, something isn't right about their numbers!
attributes.name: Natalya

attributes.content: Sonya, watch out!!
attributes.name: Anna

attributes.content: What?!
attributes.name: Sonya

attributes.content: Hand the food over!!
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.content: Graaaaahhh!!
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.content: *cough*... Guh...
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.content: (*Falls to the ground, twitching*)
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.content: ...Lada?
attributes.name: Anna

attributes.content: Don't hurt Sonya.
attributes.name: Lada

attributes.content: I won't let you...
attributes.name: Lada

attributes.content: Eek!
attributes.name: Female Student

attributes.content: She's crazy!
attributes.name: Female Student

attributes.content: She broke Andrey's neck! Be careful, everyone!
attributes.name: Male Student

attributes.content: I... I will protect everyone!
attributes.name: Lada

attributes.content: Don't hurt my friends!!
attributes.name: Lada

attributes.content: Gummy has many memories.
Good ones, bad ones.
Happy ones, sad ones.
And ones she doesn't ever want to remember, no matter what.
Gummy has hurt other people.
Was it to protect her friends, or to not get hurt herself?
Gummy does not know.
But Gummy... Gummy doesn't want to hurt other people anymore.
Gummy?
How did you fall asleep over here?
Wake up, Gummy.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Ugh... Huh...?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Wake up, Gummy.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: You're paler than a ghost. Are your wounds still bothering you?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: I think I had a nightmare.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: It doesn't hurt anymore, so don't worry. I'll be fine.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: That's good.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Huh? Istina?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Why'd you stop talking? Are you about to leave? I can leave too. What about Zima and Leto?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: No, it's not time to leave yet. You rest some more.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: The others went ahead to scout out the way. They should be back soon.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Then, I'm gonna go help too!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Not so fast.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Eh?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: One moment, Gummy. Don't start running around just yet.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Your wound's not as light as you think it is. Hold still so I can apply another dose of medicine.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: It really isn't that serious though.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Honest! I swear!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: It just... kind of stings a little bit, that's all...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Be a good girl, don't move.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Fine, if you say so!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You've taken a lot of hits.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: The scar from the previous injury seems to have gotten a bit lighter. I'm not sure if the wound this time is going to leave a mark.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: I hope it doesn't.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: The nice ladies from the Medical Department give me a super easy-to-use ointment. I rub it on every day, and the scars go right away!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Sure enough. All the scars you've gotten this last year have been treated pretty well.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: But...
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: But?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Gummy, when those bounty hunters attacked us earlier, you could've avoided getting injured, right?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Why didn't you keep chasing after them?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: When you were about to knock them out, you hesitated and held back... That's dangerous, Gummy.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: But, I...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I didn't have a choice.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Gummy...
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Instructor Dur-nar asked me about your habit before.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: The Instructor...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You're afraid, aren't you?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: ...Mhm.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I'm very afraid.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: The third time, I couldn't control myself...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I keep thinking back to that time at the school. I get nightmares about it. Even my night light doesn't help.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I... I know. You toss and turn and have trouble sleeping.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Both Zima and I know, but this is something you have to overcome by yourself, so we try not to say too much.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Mhm...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: But, Gummy, we're all worried about you.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: I'm trying my hardest.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Yes, I know. You are trying.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: You're the strongest one out of all of us.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: You don't need a night light to fall asleep anymore, right?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Though you still sometimes come running to me and Zima.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Mhm...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I'll work hard to grow up and get over my bad habits.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I also asked Amiya and Dr. Kal'tsit. Dr. Kal'tsit said that Papa and Mama have very dangerous jobs, and it'll be really hard to see them.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Do you want to go look for them?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: I do. But I can't yet.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I don't want Papa and Mama to see me like this. I don't want them to think that I'm a bad girl.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: So I can't yet.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You're not a bad girl, Gummy. You're keeping us safe.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: But, but––
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I'm not good enough yet...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I can't control myself, and I hurt other people.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Istina, what should I do?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You'll find a way.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: You might not be able to change things right away, but that's okay too. We'll here with you.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: We'll always be with you, so don't be afraid.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Istina...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Yeah! As long as you're with me, I have nothing to be afraid of!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Alright, brave little bear, don't let yourself get hurt anymore!
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Owwie, stop poking! Stop poking me, it hurts!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: So now you know it hurts?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Alright, all done applying the medicine. Zima and the others should be back soon.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Let's go check on them.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Okay!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Have a nice rest?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I'm all better now, Zima!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I treated her wounds, so they won't get in the way.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: How are things on your end?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Getting some bad vibes from that village up ahead. It's too quiet.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Might be another bounty hunter trap for all we know, so keep your guard up.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Our mission was originally to search for the missing children. My, what an unexpected turn of events.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: How did we get all these bounty hunters after us?
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Huh? They were the ones who started it!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Those bastards had two kids tied up! Weren't we looking for missing children?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Well, whatever. We already got ourselves involved, so we can't just turn a blind eye now.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: They might've gotten away last time, but they won't get that lucky again.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Just don't get too carried away. They aren't exactly easy to deal with.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Plus, those children are their hostages. We can't get them too worked up.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: If the bad guys show up again, I'll protect everyone!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Don't worry, I'm gonna send them packing!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: But, what if they don't show up?
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Um... Then, I'll flush them out?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Pain in my ass.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I have an idea.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Hello—
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Excuse me, is anyone home?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Hello—
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Huh.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Guess not...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Well, looks like we won't learn anything new here.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Guess we should get going then.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: So we're to return empty-handed? They will have to send some other operators out to try again.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Oh... But that means they'll be sending more experienced operators, right?
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Yeah, that's right!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: I heard that, err, whatsherface... Well, whatever, there's a super strong bounty hunter who can tear down entire buildings with her bare hands!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: *Sigh*...
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: (Rosalind, you're a terrible actor...)
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: (Hey, I was never good at this stuff!!)
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Let's get going!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I'm sure the senior operators will be able to catch the bad guys!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Huh?!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (I hear something! Someone's coming!)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Gummy, be careful!
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Huff...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Hold it right there!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Don't poke your noses where they don't belong, little bears.
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Or you'll regret it.
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Naw, we don't regret shit! Come try me on for size!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Save it.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hey, lemme ask you a question. These all the guys you have with you?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: What'd you do with the villagers? And those two kids you abducted?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: (They're not talking.)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I suppose we'll have to beat it out of them.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Yo, that's what I like to hear!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: It's certainly easy enough to talk big, but you do know this is different from a training simulation, right?
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: We've got this!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I'll protect everyone!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Ow!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Heavy! But I can still hold...!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Hyaaah!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Hah!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (*Slows down*)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Ugh!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Gummy!
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Gah, out of my way!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Urgh...
attributes.name: Quiet Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Dammit, we were so close...
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: We almost had that bastard!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Stay focused!
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Ngh!
attributes.name: Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Istina! Stand behind me!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You won't get through me!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Careful, Gummy!
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: I'll slow them down...
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Now's your chance, Zima!
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: On it!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Piece o' cake.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: My, such tough words from such a winded girl.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Zima!!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You're hurt! W-Was that because you took a hit for me just now?!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: It's all my fault...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Stop your blubbering already, it's annoying.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Yeah, she obviously got way too careless! It had nothing to do with you, Gummy!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: But still!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: We've got more pressing issues on our hands right now.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Hey, you! What's the play? You're the only one left.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Spit it out. What happened to the village? And what'd you do with the kids?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: If you're not gonna talk...
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: If you're not gonna talk, then, we're gonna pull out all your hair and teeth!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (Probably don't have to go that far.)
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Heh. You're just a bunch of runts.
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Watch your damn mouth!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: So you can deliver a beating or two. So what?
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: You wanna find those kids?
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Sure do!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Out with it already!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Haha... dumb runt.
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Too bad for you, I'm the only one who knows where those kids are.
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Something happens to me and you'll never find them.
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: You'll talk, if you know what's good for you.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: In a situation like this, I would expect you to try negotiating with us.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Let us go.
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Then we'll take those kids back to the village. As for the other stuff, you mind your own business.
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: That's all you got?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Sucks for you, but–– no deal.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Why would we negotiate with a loser like you?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Yeah, yeah!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (He went quiet.)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (Is he gonna do that thing where you bite your tongue until you die?)
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: (This is tricky, but we don't necessarily have to force it out of him...)
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Just smack him around a couple more times and we'll be good!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Ah, you're not supposed to raise your voice like that, Zima!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: How dare you treat me like this...
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: ––You damned runts!
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Watch out!
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Zima!!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: What?! Woah!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: You son of a bitch!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: A bitch, huh?
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Of course I'm gonna play every card in my hand!
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Now die!
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: Sonya!
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.text: Gummy will protect everyone, no matter what.

attributes.content: Damn you, little—!
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: *cough*... Guh...
attributes.name: Sullen Bounty Hunter

attributes.content: I won't let you...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I won't let you hurt Sonya!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: One more hit...!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Wait, Gummy! I'm fine! Calm down!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: We still need to find out where the kids are!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I, I––
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Gummy... Are you okay?
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Holy shit... Is he dead?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: No, he's still alive.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: My dear Rosalind, would you mind helping me carry this gentleman over there? I'm going to stop the bleeding, then help him 'wake up.'
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Sure thing... But why are you calling me that? It's freakin' me out.
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Fine, fine. Come now.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Zima, your wound... There's blood! I, I'll help you bandage it!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I'm sorry...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I'm sorry, Zima, Istina. I... messed up again...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Cut the crap.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: What'd you mess up? You saved me. I didn't even have a chance to thank you.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: But...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: No buts.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Gummy, you were scared, but you still protected us.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Exactly.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Besides... I know exactly how strong you are. If you really bashed his head in with all your strength, his brains would be splattered all over the ground.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: But he––
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: He's fine. Don't worry.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Actually, can't you smack him again to wake him up?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: It's okay...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I, I kept things under control...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You did.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: During that last swing, you managed to hold back your power. I saw it, clear as day.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Gummy.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Come here.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: You too, Zima.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: You don't need us?
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: What are you playing at?
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Settle down! Stop crowding around me!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Amidst the chaos, the children of the Ursus Student Self-Governing Group form an intimate gathering.

Istina takes Gummy's left hand, while Zima takes her right hand. The little bears hold hands, their foreheads touching. Nobody backs away even when their cheeks get itchy brushing against their friends' hair.
Gummy presses her head against her friends', their foreheads gently touching just as they always do when they play together.
And her friends press back against her intimately.
Gummy, do you remember what I said before?
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: You're doing great.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Don't be afraid. We'll always be with you.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: That's right, you heard her! You did a great job, Gummy! That last block was great!
attributes.name: Leto

attributes.content: Hehe, you're almost stronger than a certain someone who can't control her temper.
attributes.name: Rosa

attributes.content: Huuuuh? You talkin' about me?!
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: Pfft...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Zima, don't start jumping around! Your wounds!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Have I...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Have I really done it? Did I really manage to control my strength?
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: You did. You held back.
attributes.name: Zima

attributes.content: I do think we'll be able to wake that fellow up pretty soon. Then we can ask where the children are.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Trust me. I have ways of making him talk.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: Gummy, you not only protected us, but also those children.
attributes.name: Istina

attributes.content: I... kept things under control...
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I did it!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I'll have to bring this along, and that... Oh, and some bread too!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Phew... I've finally finished packing my bag.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Papa, Mama, Lada is going to go find you two soon!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Even though Dr. Kal'tsit said it'll be hard, I still want to give it a try!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: By the way, I don't have to hesitate when hitting people anymore... Because I know I'll be able to control my strength at the end!
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: I won't be a burden on my friends... and I won't be a burden on Papa and Mama.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Thanks to them, even though I still have nightmares, I'm not so scared anymore.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Papa, Mama, I'm having a great time here.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Oh, I have to go meet up with my friends now. This will be my first time going out on my own, but I'll definitely come back. I know they'll be waiting for me.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Phew.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: Alright, I'll end the recording right there.
attributes.name: Gummy

attributes.content: ––Let's gooo!
attributes.name: Gummy
